The evidence with the title 'Fact-checking Rick Scott at CPAC | politifact Florida ' says Feb 17, 2012  ... Scott said Florida 's economy was on the mend, throwing out this statistic: "in my first year in office , unemployment has dropped more than 2 percentage points, down from 12 percent to 9.9 percent , the second-largest drop in the nation," he said . He also said he was working hard to reduce government. 
